            <thetext>Reported issue from Tobi Oetiker: 

&quot;I am using the qooxdoo SelectBox ... I use this.tr to make the
ListItems values translatable. This works fine as fahr as the
content of the dropdown is concerned. But as soon as I select an
item, the original language gets displayed in on the SelectBox
button.&quot;

This code reproduce the issue:
var selectbox = new qx.ui.form.SelectBox();
var item1 = new qx.ui.form.ListItem(this.tr(&quot;Item 1&quot;));
var item2 = new qx.ui.form.ListItem(this.tr(&quot;Item 2&quot;));
      
selectbox.add(item1);
selectbox.add(item2);
      
var doc = this.getRoot();
doc.add(selectbox, {left: 100, top: 50});
      
qx.locale.Manager.getInstance().setLocale(&quot;de&quot;);

To reproduce the issue, change the selection on the SelectBox.</thetext>
